Private Events
/$
$
Host Your Perfect Event at Spill
No matter the occasion, Spill is the ideal venue to host your private party or special event. Whether you’re celebrating a birthday, anniversary, fundraiser, corporate gathering, holiday party, baby shower, retirement, or even a monthly book club, our dedicated team is here to ensure your event is a memorable success.
​
Relax and enjoy your time—we can take care of every detail for you, or simply reserve the perfect space and let Spill’s unique atmosphere set the tone.
​
Looking to include food? We’ve got you covered! We offer custom grazing tables and a wide variety of platters tailored to your needs.
​
Let Spill be the backdrop for your next celebration—contact us today to start planning!
